               <text>
                  <br/>
                  <br/>
                  <br/>
                  <br/>
                  <br/>
                  <paragraph>Meprobamate Tablets USP 200 mg are white to off white, round, biconvex, uncoated tablets debossed with "L125" on one side and break line on other side.</paragraph>
